<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<title>All the relevant tech events in Berlin</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
<h1>All the relevant tech events in Berlin</h1>
<p><a href="faq.html#get-my-events-list">How to get my events listed</a> and <a href="background.html">why are we doing this?</a>
<div class="table-responsive-md">
  <table class="table">
    <thead class="thead-dark">
      <tr>
        <th scope="col">When</th>
        <th scope="col">What</th>
        <th scope="col">Who</th>
        <th scope="col">Where</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for event in events %}
          <tr>
          <td scope="row">{{ event.local_date }} {{ event.local_time }}</td>
          <td><a href="{{ event.link }}">{{ event.name }}</a></td>
          <td>{{ event.group.name }}</td>
          <td>{% if event.venue %} {{ event.venue.address_1 }} {% endif %}</td>
          </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
<p>Site generated on {{ now }}
<p>&copy; 2018 by Nils Magnus and Dirk Gomez. <a href="impressum.html">Impressum</a>
</body>
</html>
